text: Rodolfo Guaves (born 21 August 1953) is a Filipino former cyclist. He competed in the sprint and 1000m time trial events at the 1984 Summer Olympics and 1982 Asian Games. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Filipino male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the Philippines Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Asian Games medalists in cycling Category:Cyclists at the 1982 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 1982 Asian Games Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for the Philippines
